r-id=3D"1203279740" data-linked-resource-container-version=3D"16" alt=3D"" =
width=3D"468" height=3D"375"></span></p>
</div>
</div>
</div></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style=3D"text-align: left;" class=3D"confluenceTd"><h2 id=3D"Stepstobui=
ldaKafkaProducer-2"><strong>2</strong></h2></td>
<td style=3D"text-align: left;" class=3D"confluenceTd">
<div class=3D"content-wrapper">
<h2 id=3D"StepstobuildaKafkaProducer-AddProducer"><strong>Add Producer&nbsp=
;</strong></h2>
<p>Add producer capability to the API component.</p>
<ul>
<li>Go to the component repository in cmd prompt.</li>
<li>Add producer capability by running 'enable' command and following the s=
creen prompts.</li>
</ul>
<p>&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;</p>
<div class=3D"code panel pdl" style=3D"border-width: 1px;">
<div class=3D"codeHeader panelHeader pdl" style=3D"border-bottom-width: 1px=
;"><b>Add producer capability</b>
</div>
<div class=3D"codeContent panelContent pdl">
<pre class=3D"syntaxhighlighter-pre" data-syntaxhighlighter-params=3D"brush=
: bash; gutter: false; theme: Confluence" data-theme=3D"Confluence">mesh en=
able -a kafkaProducer</pre>
</div>
</div>
<p><br></p>
</div><p><br></p>
<div id=3D"expander-1008299524" class=3D"expand-container">
<div role=3D"heading" aria-level=3D"6" id=3D"expander-control-1008299524" c=
lass=3D"expand-control"><button type=3D"button" id=3D"expand-button-1008299=
524" class=3D"aui-button aui-button-link aui-button-link-icon-text" aria-ex=
panded=3D"true" aria-controls=3D"expander-content-1008299524"><span class=
=3D"expand-icon aui-icon aui-icon-small aui-iconfont-chevron-down" aria-hid=
den=3D"true"></span><span class=3D"expand-control-text conf-macro-render">S=
ee Example:</span></button>
</div>
<div role=3D"region" id=3D"expander-content-1008299524" class=3D"expand-con=
tent" aria-labelledby=3D"expand-button-1008299524">
<p><span class=3D"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper"><img class=3D"confluenc=
