<td style=3D"text-align: left;" colspan=3D"1" class=3D"confluenceTd"><h2 id=
=3D"StepstobuildaKafkaProducer-5"><strong>5</strong></h2></td>
<td style=3D"text-align: left;" colspan=3D"1" class=3D"confluenceTd">
<div class=3D"content-wrapper">
<h2 id=3D"StepstobuildaKafkaProducer-CreateProducerInstance"><strong>Create=
 Producer&nbsp;</strong><strong>Instance</strong></h2>
<p>Create a producer instance :</p>
<ul>
<li>Westpac Mesh Kafka producer library<span style=3D"color: rgb(23,43,77);=
">&nbsp;provides a generic producer factory(<span>&nbsp;</span></span><code=
>WdpKafkaProducerFactory&lt;V&gt;</code>, where <code>V</code> is the gener=
ated Avro type for your Topic schema<span style=3D"color: rgb(23,43,77);">)=
 which should be used to create a<span>&nbsp;</span></span><code>WdpKafkaPr=
oducer&lt;&gt;</code>&nbsp;for your specific class<span style=3D"color: rgb=
(23,43,77);">.</span>&nbsp; This producer factory is auto-configured with t=
he producer library and made available to auto-wire.&nbsp;</li>
</ul>
<ul>
<li><span style=3D"color: rgb(23,43,77);">Auto wire the producer factory pr=
ovided by the producer library with the event record type as type reference=
.</span></li>
<li><span style=3D"color: rgb(23,43,77);">Create an instance of<span>&nbsp;=
</span><code>WdpKafkaProducer&lt;&gt;&nbsp;</code>using the '<code>createPr=
oducer'</code>&nbsp;method which takes the logical name of the target topic=
.</span></li>
</ul>
<p><br></p>
<div id=3D"expander-2051945252" class=3D"expand-container">
<div role=3D"heading" aria-level=3D"6" id=3D"expander-control-2051945252" c=
lass=3D"expand-control"><button type=3D"button" id=3D"expand-button-2051945=
252" class=3D"aui-button aui-button-link aui-button-link-icon-text" aria-ex=
panded=3D"true" aria-controls=3D"expander-content-2051945252"><span class=
=3D"expand-icon aui-icon aui-icon-small aui-iconfont-chevron-down" aria-hid=
den=3D"true"></span><span class=3D"expand-control-text conf-macro-render">S=
ee Example:</span></button>
</div>
<div role=3D"region" id=3D"expander-content-2051945252" class=3D"expand-con=
tent" aria-labelledby=3D"expand-button-2051945252">
<div class=3D"code panel pdl" style=3D"border-width: 1px;">
<div class=3D"codeHeader panelHeader pdl" style=3D"border-bottom-width: 1px=
;"><b>Creating WdpKafkaProducer Bean in ClientConfig.java</b>
</div>
<div class=3D"codeContent panelContent pdl">
<pre class=3D"syntaxhighlighter-pre" data-syntaxhighlighter-params=3D"brush=
: java; gutter: false; theme: Confluence" data-theme=3D"Confluence">@Bean
WdpKafkaProducer&lt;ReferenceEvent&gt; referenceEventProducer(@Autowired Wd=
pKafkaProducerFactory&lt;ReferenceEvent&gt; referenceEventProducerFactory){
    return referenceEventProducerFactory.createProducer(referenceEventTopic=
);
}</pre>
</div>
</div>
</div>
</div>
</div></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style=3D"text-align: left;" colspan=3D"1" class=3D"confluenceTd"><h2 id=
=3D"StepstobuildaKafkaProducer-6"><strong>6</strong></h2></td>
<td style=3D"text-align: left;" colspan=3D"1" class=3D"confluenceTd">
<div class=3D"content-wrapper">
<h2 id=3D"StepstobuildaKafkaProducer-Optional:CreatingMultipleevents"><stro=
ng>Optional: Creating Multiple events</strong></h2>
<p><br></p>
<ul>
<li>To produce multiple events (with different record types) to multiple to=
pics,&nbsp;<span style=3D"color: rgb(23,43,77);">create another bean with t=
he specific Avro type and wire it in your implementation.</span><span style=
=3D"color: rgb(23,43,77);">&nbsp;You can repeat this for as many topics as =
you wish to publish to.</span>&nbsp;</li>
</ul>
<p>&nbsp; &nbsp;</p>
<div id=3D"expander-1939386700" class=3D"expand-container">
<div role=3D"heading" aria-level=3D"6" id=3D"expander-control-1939386700" c=
lass=3D"expand-control"><button type=3D"button" id=3D"expand-button-1939386=
700" class=3D"aui-button aui-button-link aui-button-link-icon-text" aria-ex=
panded=3D"true" aria-controls=3D"expander-content-1939386700"><span class=
=3D"expand-icon aui-icon aui-icon-small aui-iconfont-chevron-down" aria-hid=
den=3D"true"></span><span class=3D"expand-control-text conf-macro-render">S=
ee Example:</span></button>
</div>
<div role=3D"region" id=3D"expander-content-1939386700" class=3D"expand-con=
tent" aria-labelledby=3D"expand-button-1939386700">
<div class=3D"code panel pdl" style=3D"border-width: 1px;">
<div class=3D"codeHeader panelHeader pdl" style=3D"border-bottom-width: 1px=
;"><b>Creating Multiple WdpKafkaProducer Beans</b>
</div>
<div class=3D"codeContent panelContent pdl">
<pre class=3D"syntaxhighlighter-pre" data-syntaxhighlighter-params=3D"brush=
: java; gutter: false; theme: Confluence" data-theme=3D"Confluence">@Bean
WdpKafkaProducer&lt;Event1&gt; event1Producer(@Autowired WdpKafkaProducerFa=
ctory&lt;Event1&gt; event1ProducerFactory){
    return event1ProducerFactory.createProducer(event1Topic);
}
=20
@Bean
WdpKafkaProducer&lt;Event2&gt; event2Producer(@Autowired WdpKafkaProducerFa=
ctory&lt;Event2&gt; event2ProducerFactory){
    return event2ProducerFactory.createProducer(event2Topic);
}</pre>
</div>
</div>
</div>
</div>
</div></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td colspan=3D"1" class=3D"confluenceTd"><h2 id=3D"StepstobuildaKafkaProduc=
er-7"><strong>7</strong></h2></td>
<td colspan=3D"1" class=3D"confluenceTd">
<div class=3D"content-wrapper">
<h2 id=3D"StepstobuildaKafkaProducer-UpdateProducerInstance"><strong>Update=
 Producer Instance</strong></h2>
<p><code style=3D"text-align: left;">WdpKafkaProducer&lt;V&gt;</code><span =
style=3D"color: rgb(23,43,77);">&nbsp; created in step 5 infers physical to=
pic name from the logical name of the topic - provided while creating the p=
roducer instance. Inject the instance of&nbsp; ''<span>&nbsp;</span><code s=
tyle=3D"text-align: left;">WdpKafkaProducer&lt;V&gt;'&nbsp;</code>bean in y=
our API implementation class and invoke the '<code style=3D"text-align: lef=
t;">sendEvent'</code><span>&nbsp;</span>method in the producer instance cre=
ated above to post an event to the configured topic.</span></p>
<p><br></p>
<p><br></p>
<div id=3D"expander-450408516" class=3D"expand-container">
<div role=3D"heading" aria-level=3D"6" id=3D"expander-control-450408516" cl=
ass=3D"expand-control"><button type=3D"button" id=3D"expand-button-45040851=
6" class=3D"aui-button aui-button-link aui-button-link-icon-text" aria-expa=
nded=3D"true" aria-controls=3D"expander-content-450408516"><span class=3D"e=
xpand-icon aui-icon aui-icon-small aui-iconfont-chevron-down" aria-hidden=
=3D"true"></span><span class=3D"expand-control-text conf-macro-render">See =
Example:</span></button>
</div>
<div role=3D"region" id=3D"expander-content-450408516" class=3D"expand-cont=
ent" aria-labelledby=3D"expand-button-450408516">
<div class=3D"code panel pdl" style=3D"border-width: 1px;">
<div class=3D"codeHeader panelHeader pdl" style=3D"border-bottom-width: 1px=
;"><b>Autowiring and Event publishing sample</b>
</div>
<div class=3D"codeContent panelContent pdl">
<pre class=3D"syntaxhighlighter-pre" data-syntaxhighlighter-params=3D"brush=
: java; gutter: false; theme: Confluence" data-theme=3D"Confluence">@Servic=
e
@javax.annotation.Generated(value =3D "io.swagger.codegen.languages.JavaJer=
seyServerCodegen", date =3D "2019-07-16T16:54:35.170+10:00")
public class PublishEventApiServiceImpl extends PublishEventApiService {
    @Autowired
    private WdpKafkaProducer&lt;ReferenceEvent&gt; referenceEventProducer;

    @Override
    public Response postEventToTopic(String xMessageId, String xAppCorrelat=
ionId, String xOrganisationId, String xOriginatingSystemId, String xConsume=
rType, PublishEventRequest publishEventRequest,  String xUserId, String xUs=
erIdScheme, SecurityContext securityContext) throws NotFoundException {
        try {
          =20
            EventHeader eventHeader =3D EventHeader.newBuilder()
                    .setEventId(UUID.randomUUID().toString())
                    .setAppCorrelationId(xAppCorrelationId)
                    .setBrandSilo(EnumBrandSilo.Other)
                    .setOrganisationId(EnumOrganisationId.valueOf(xOrganisa=
tionId))
                    .setOriginatingSystemId(xOriginatingSystemId)
                    .setProducerId(API_NAME)
                    .setConsumerType(EnumConsumerType.valueOf(xConsumerType=
))
                    .setUserId(xUserId).setUserIdScheme(xUserIdScheme!=3Dnu=
ll?
                            EnumUserIdScheme.valueOf(String.valueOf(xUserId=
Scheme)):null)
                    .setOccurredOn(Instant.now().toEpochMilli())
                    .setDetectedOn(Instant.now().toEpochMilli())
                    .setExpiresOn(Instant.now().toEpochMilli())
                    .build();
            ReferenceEvent referenceEvent =3D buildReferenceEvent(eventHead=
er, publishEventRequest);

            SendResult&lt;String, ReferenceEvent&gt; sendResult =3D referen=
ceEventProducer.sendEvent(xMessageId, UUID.randomUUID().toString(), referen=
ceEvent);

            Response res =3D Response.created(null).entity(buildResponse(se=
ndResult.getRecordMetadata())).build();

            return res;
        } catch (Exception  e) {
          =20
            return createErrorResponse(e, Response.Status.INTERNAL_SERVER_E=
RROR, 10003, "Catch all exception ");
        }

    }

</pre>
