<td colspan=3D"1" class=3D"confluenceTd"><h2 id=3D"StepstobuildaKafkaProduc=
er-8"><strong>8</strong></h2></td>
<td colspan=3D"1" class=3D"confluenceTd"><h2 id=3D"StepstobuildaKafkaProduc=
er-Optional:"><strong>Optional:</strong></h2><p><br></p><p>While most of th=
e properties&nbsp;<span style=3D"color: rgb(23,43,77);">required for connec=
ting to Kafka brokers are auto-configured by the Westpac Mesh Kafka produce=
r library, users can use&nbsp;<strong>kafka-producer.properties </strong>to=
 supplement the producer config.</span></p><p><strong><span style=3D"color:=
 rgb(23,43,77);">Note</span></strong><span style=3D"color: rgb(23,43,77);">=
: '</span><span style=3D"color: rgb(23,43,77);">kafka-producer.properties '=
should not be used to inject any properties other than Kafka producer confi=
guration or override Westpac Mesh injected properties. For a full list of M=
esh injected properties refer <a href=3D"https://bitbucket.srv.westpac.com.=
au/projects/WDPCOM/repos/lib-westpac-digital-platform-springkafkaproducer/b=
rowse/Readme.md" class=3D"external-link" rel=3D"nofollow">read.me</a>.</spa=
n></p><p><br></p></td>
