er-KafkaProducerandSwimlaneSupport"><strong>Kafka Producer and Swimlane&nbs=
p;</strong><strong>Support</strong></h2><p>Kafka Producer and Swimlane supp=
ort</p><p>Westpac Mesh treats Kafka producer as a capability that enriches =
an API to produce messages to a Kafka topic. Just like any other Westpac Me=
sh API, Kafka producer API also supports virtual swimlanes. The process to =
enroll, deploy, and undeploy a swimlane is the same as that of a normal API=
. Refer to&nbsp;Mesh Developer tools <a href=3D"https://confluence.srv.west=
pac.com.au/display/WDPIPAAS/Mesh+Developer+Tools" rel=3D"nofollow">document=
ation</a>&nbsp;for swimlane operations.&nbsp;&nbsp;</p></td>
</tr>
<tr>
