er-12"><strong>12</strong></h2></td>
<td colspan=3D"1" class=3D"confluenceTd">
<div class=3D"content-wrapper">
<h2 id=3D"StepstobuildaKafkaProducer-TestingProducerCodeLocally"><strong>Te=
sting Producer Code Locally</strong></h2>
<p>A producer can be run from on your local workstation, just like any othe=
r API.</p>
<p><strong>For Confluent cloud</strong>:</p>
<p>The process for testing your producer that connects to a topic migrated =
to Confluent cloud is by using generic DEV credentials (early adopter funct=
ional account) which has access to all topics in the DEV cluster. Early ado=
pter credentials for connecting to DEV Kafka cluster is provided in this pa=
ge: <a href=3D"/display/MD/Early+Adopter+Credentials+for+Confluent+Cloud+DE=
V+cluster">Early Adopter Credentials for Confluent Cloud DEV cluster</a></p=
>
<p>Follow the below steps to configure:</p>
<ul>
<li>Create a file named 'wdp-kafka.properties' in the env/local folder.</li=
>
<li>Update the file as shown in below sample titled wdp-kafka.properties.</=
li>
<li>Add the topic and group ID details to the file. This can be retrieved f=
rom the Configure access stage logs of the pipeline in producer deployment.=
</li>
<li>Create a file named 'wdp-kafka-secrets.properties' in secrets/local fol=
der.</li>
<li>Update the file as shown in below sample titled wdp-kafka-secrets.prope=
rties</li>
<li>Run the producer normally using 'mesh run' command.</li>
</ul>
<p><br></p>
<div class=3D"code panel pdl" style=3D"border-width: 1px;">
<div class=3D"codeHeader panelHeader pdl hide-border-bottom" style=3D"borde=
r-bottom-width: 1px;">
<b class=3D"code-title">wdp-kafka.properties</b><span class=3D"collapse-sou=
rce expand-control" style=3D"display:none;"><span class=3D"expand-control-i=
con icon">&nbsp;</span><span class=3D"expand-control-text">Expand source</s=
pan></span><span class=3D"collapse-spinner-wrapper"></span>
</div>
<div class=3D"codeContent panelContent pdl hide-toolbar">
<pre class=3D"syntaxhighlighter-pre" data-syntaxhighlighter-params=3D"brush=
: js; gutter: true; theme: Confluence; collapse: true" data-theme=3D"Conflu=
ence">security.protocol=3DSASL_SSL
ssl.enabled.protocols=3DTLSv1.2
ssl.protocol=3DTLSv1.2
sasl.mechanism=3DPLAIN
client.dns.lookup=3Duse_all_dns_ips
session.timeout.ms=3D45000
delivery.timeout.ms=3D31000
request.timeout.ms=3D30000
acks=3Dall

basic.auth.credentials.source=3DUSER_INFO
bootstrap.servers=3Dlkc-381q32-g42l2p.australiaeast.azure.glb.confluent.clo=
ud:9092
schema.registry.url=3Dhttps://wdp-registry.api.srv.westpac.com.au
# Below details can be retrieved from the producer deployment logs to DEV (=
Kafka - Configure access stage)
group.id=3D&lt;groupid&gt;
&lt;topicName&gt;=3Dev-&lt;topicName&gt;

</pre>
</div>
</div>
<div class=3D"code panel pdl" style=3D"border-width: 1px;">
<div class=3D"codeHeader panelHeader pdl hide-border-bottom" style=3D"borde=
r-bottom-width: 1px;">
<b class=3D"code-title">wdp-kafka-secrets.properties</b><span class=3D"coll=
apse-source expand-control" style=3D"display:none;"><span class=3D"expand-c=
ontrol-icon icon">&nbsp;</span><span class=3D"expand-control-text">Expand s=
ource</span></span><span class=3D"collapse-spinner-wrapper"></span>
</div>
<div class=3D"codeContent panelContent pdl hide-toolbar">
