: js; gutter: true; theme: Confluence; collapse: true" data-theme=3D"Conflu=
ence">sasl.jaas.config=3Dorg.apache.kafka.common.security.plain.PlainLoginM=
odule required \
    username=3D"XLSZGRSF5Q523R2Y" \
    password=3D"S9p1mnOD87AvKJiCaifcC+qXA9vRGF75f1GvMMDCu1Dwf6ZRUg9oboOb8Mo=
/J82v";
basic.auth.user.info=3DWLEMXWUD4UQT36EA:UKXm0BBso7WgiOJhKaAQ7S5H1mLHE5QCbJv=
BlILxwYrPK6ukBEu2kb5jFpShE4WR</pre>
